EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

This Order appoints 6th November 2020 as the day on which Section 97 and 
Section 100 of the Regulated Professions (Health and Social Care) (Amendment) 
Act 2020 come into operation. These relate to the registration of medical 
practitioners under the Medical Practitioners Act 2007.
